==French==

===Verb===
'''répondre'''
# (intransitive) To [[reply]], to [[answer]]
#:''Tu dois répondre aux questions que je te pose.''
#::''You must answer the questions I put to you.''

====Usage note====
''Répondre'' is followed by ''[[à]]'' to make it transitive

